description: Wise Group AB engages in the activities specializing in recruitment, consultancy, and other services within human resources (HR). The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 551 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2007-04-16. The company is a parent company within the Wise Group (the Group). The Group offers Web-based services within process descriptions and document support, expertize and capacity within professional consultancy services, as well as recruitment, management outplacement and career coaching. As of December 31, 2011, the Company had six subsidiaries, which operated as separate business segments, namely Netsurvey Bolinder AB, responsible for employee and customer surveys; Wise Consulting AB, responsible for coaching, conversions and human resources (HR) consulting; Wise OnLine AB, offering online services for information and decision support in the HR area; K2 Search AB, a search and executive search company; Wise Professionals AB, engaged in the recruitment of skilled staff for advanced services, and Talentum HR AB, offering consultancy, guidance, education and seminars.
